The paper deals with unsupervised ensemble learning, which is a subfield of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the construction of a statistical model to allow for dependencies between classifiers, which is a topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of ensemble learning in computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL) is also mentioned. Finally, the paper deals with the estimation of classifier accuracies, which is a topic in data science (cs.DS).
